                                <h1>David P. Boder Interviews Fela Nichthauser; August 1, 1946; Fontenay-aux-Roses, France</h1>
                                            <ul class="transcripts">
    <li class="interview_home">
        <a href="interviewee?doc=nichthauserF">
            Interview homepage
        </a>
